---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const posts = Array.from({ length: 27 }, (_, i) => i + 1);
---

<BaseLayout
	locale="en"
	title="Arte Arabia">
	<section class="project-hero">
		<div
			class="hero-bg"
			style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a2e 0%,#16213e 50%,#0f3460 100%)">
		</div>
		<div class="hero-overlay"></div>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<a
					href="/#results"
					class="back-link"
					><svg
						width="20"
						height="20"
						viewBox="0 0 20 20"
						fill="none"
						><path
							d="M15 5L5 10L15 15"
							stroke="currentColor"
							stroke-width="1.5"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
						></path></svg
					>Back</a
				>
				<h1 class="project-title">Arte Arabia</h1>
				<p class="project-tagline">WooCommerce store with 100% custom code</p>
				<p class="project-context">E-commerce / Retail — Mexico</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="project-section">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="section-label-text"><i>01</i> Problem</span>
			<p class="project-body">
				Arte Arabia is a store selling items from Arabia, Morocco, Turkey,
				Persia, Palestine, the Emirates and other corners of the Middle East:
				decor, incense, perfumes, jewelry, fashion and gifts. They needed a
				transactional website that reflected the visual richness of their
				products, functioned as both catalog and online store, and represented
				the identity of their physical locations in Querétaro and Guadalajara.
				Most off-the-shelf themes failed to capture the Middle Eastern aesthetic
				the brand required.
			</p>
			<div class="project-tags">
				<span class="tag">WordPress</span><span class="tag">WooCommerce</span
				><span class="tag">PHP</span><span class="tag">UI/UX</span
				><span class="tag">Social Media</span><span class="tag">Video</span>
			</div>

			<span class="section-label-text mb-4 mt-5">Social media posts</span>
			<div class="project-grid-3">
				{posts.filter(n => n !== 16).map(n => (
					<img
						src={`/projects/artearabia/${n}.jpg`}
						alt={`Post ${n}`}
						class="img-fluid"
						style="width:100%;border-radius:8px"
					/>
				))}
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="project-section-alt" style="position:relative;overflow:hidden">
		<video autoplay loop muted playsinline
			style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;z-index:0">
			<source src="/projects/artearabia/perfumesArabes.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
		</video>
		<div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;backdrop-filter:blur(15px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(15px);z-index:1"></div>
		<div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:2">
			<span class="section-label-text"><i>02</i> System & Approach</span>
			<p class="project-body">
				A WordPress + WooCommerce site was built with a 100% custom theme —
				no theme purchased from Envato and no prefabricated templates. Every
				line of code was written to order to reflect the brand's visual
				identity.
			</p>
			<p class="project-body">
				The site handles a full catalog with categories including Fashion,
				Incense & Aromas, Rings & Jewelry, Arabic Perfumes, Home and Gifts. It
				includes secure payments via Stripe (Visa, Mastercard), personalized
				attention through WhatsApp and Facebook, and synchronization with two
				physical stores.
			</p>
			<p class="project-body">
				In addition to the website, social media posts were designed to
				maintain visual identity on Instagram and Facebook, promoting products
				and collections.
			</p>
			<div class="project-process">
				<strong>Deliverables:</strong> transactional website + social media content
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="project-gallery">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="section-label-text mb-4">Website — Screenshots</span>
			<img
				src="/projects/artearabia/FireShot Capture 373 - Homepage - Arte Arabia Tienda - [artearabia.com].png"
				alt="Arte Arabia homepage"
				class="img-fluid"
				style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:2rem"
			/>
			<img
				src="/projects/artearabia/FireShot Capture 374 - Anillos, Pulseras y bisurería archivos - Arte Arabia Tienda_ - [artearabia.com].png"
				alt="Arte Arabia category page"
				class="img-fluid"
				style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:2rem"
			/>

			<span class="section-label-text mb-4 mt-5">Promotional videos</span>
			<div class="project-grid-2">
				<video controls class="img-fluid" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px">
					<source src="/projects/artearabia/inciensos.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
				</video>
				<video controls class="img-fluid" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px">
					<source src="/projects/artearabia/perfumesArabes.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
				</video>
			</div>

		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="project-result">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="result-box">
				<h2>Result</h2><p>
					Fully functional online store with 100% custom code that faithfully
					reflects the brand identity. Stripe payment integration, multi-channel
					attention (WhatsApp, Facebook), and coordinated presence between
					physical stores and website. Digital catalog of hundreds of products
					with intuitive navigation and authentic Middle Eastern aesthetic.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="project-section">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="section-label-text"><i>03</i> Learnings</span><p
				class="project-body">
				WooCommerce e-commerce allows total creative freedom when custom code
				is written. Prefabricated themes limit brand identity. Building from
				scratch requires more work but the result is a site that truly
				represents the business. Social media content extended the visual
				identity beyond the website, creating a consistent brand experience
				across all channels.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<style>
		.tag { color: black; }
	</style>
</BaseLayout>